@nameref
@NAMEREF

Create, alter, or delete named references to DBREFs. To use a named reference, prefix the name with $ and use it anywhere a DBREF is a valid parameter.

Syntax: @nameref <name> <dbref number>
        @nameref #list                 list all entries in the nameref table
        @nameref #delete <name>        delete the entry in the nameref table with the given name           
        @nameref #clear                clear the entire table

